thread.title: Students demand gun reform in nationwide walkout

title: Students demand gun reform in nationwide walkout
text:
Students demand gun reform in nationwide walkout 11:09am EDT - 01:14 
From coast-to-coast, students spill out of their classrooms chanting slogans like ‘enough is enough’ during a protest against gun violence prompted by a deadly rampage at a Florida high school last month.
